word_mean_info__list.difference: 指暂时中断以待某种条件的实现。
正式用词，语气强于postpone，多指故意拖延。
正式用词，语气较强，多指有安排的延期，常指明延期到一定的时间。
指把时间延长至超过正常或通常的限度。
普通用词，多指因外界原因推迟或耽误，也可指有意推迟。
口语用词，与postpone同义，但较通俗。

bilingual.source: The increase in construction costs caused a delay in the project.
bilingual.target: 工程造价的增加导致了项目延期。

bilingual.source: The news of the delay dampens our excitement about the project.
bilingual.target: 延期的消息抑制了我们对项目的兴奋。
然而,那次延期几乎令波音公司破产.

bilingual.source: Uses: Delay and for fuel in pyrotechnics and strong deoxidizer.
bilingual.target: 用途：延期药和烟火剂中作可燃物和强脱氧剂。

bilingual.source: The design of the critical components and the effect of the device used in mixing the delay composition show that the device is fit for the special mixing process for the delay composition.
bilingual.target: 其关键部件设计以及在延期药混制上的应用效果表明，该设备适用于延期药的特种混药工艺。

bilingual.source: We wish to apologize once again for the delay in delivery.
bilingual.target: 对于此次的延期交货我们再次向您表示道歉.

bilingual.source: The Russian government says it wants to delay payment on its debt.
bilingual.target: 俄罗斯政府则表示希望延期清偿该债务.

bilingual.source: European Council head Donald Tusk said today that he supports the delay.
bilingual.target: 欧洲理事会主席图斯克称他支持延期。

bilingual.source: They regarded the request for delay as merely the prelude to his recantation .
bilingual.target: 也认为他延期的请求就是他反悔的先声。

list.abstract: delay（英 [dɪˈleɪ]，美 [dɪˈleɪ]），英语单词，作动词为使搁置；使延迟；延迟。作名词为延迟的时间；延时；拖延。短语搭配有delay line（延迟线）。例句为“Delay is likely to prejudice the child's welfare（延误可能损害这孩子的幸福）”。 delay相关近义词有wait等，相关反义词有rush。
Delay组合，是中国风原创组合，成员有吉他手黄迪，键盘手惠雷。2010年参加湖南卫视举办的《快乐男声》比赛，长相老成的他们成为最大的黑马，没有年龄优势，DELAY最大的与众不同就是他们原创和独特复古曲风。获得全国第11名。

yingyinNormal.en: Are they running it? No. I got a two-week delay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们已经在调查了吗？没有，我争取了延迟了两周。

yingyinNormal.en: Your Honor, they are trying to delay an execution.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法官阁下，他们是要拖延死刑时间。

yingyinNormal.en: Either way, there's no reason to delay this execution anymore.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不管怎么说，都没任何理由推迟死刑了。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you, Mrs Hughes. We mustn't delay you. Can you send Anna up? Of course, m'lady.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢你，休斯太太，不耽误你工作了，能叫安娜上来吗？好的，小姐。

yingyinNormal.en: What the hell is your delay, Captain? You supposed to begin that assault 10 minutes ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你到底拖延什么，上尉？你应该在10分钟前开始进攻。

yingyinNormal.en: Upload the link. Return to LaGuardia. Now with an added 35-second delay in response time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 开启传输，回到拉瓜迪亚机场，现在加上35秒的反应时间。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm not gonna delay this execution any longer. How soon can you have that nurse available?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我决定不再推迟刑期了，护士什么时候能出庭作证?

yingyinNormal.en: Do you want to get the judge on the line? What, and delay this even more? Go ahead, Eddie.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你想连线法官吗? 干嘛?让你们拖延更久吗? 继续，艾迪。

yingyinNormal.en: Unacceptable. The delay would result in tomorrow morning's bowel movement occurring at work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不予通过，吃饭太晚会造成明天早晨的大肠蠕动出现在工作时间。

yingyinNormal.en: Remember, we agreed to delay discussion on compensation? I thought we should talk about that now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 记得吗？我们同意推迟到赔偿时再谈，我认为我们应该现在就谈。

yingyinNormal.en: She seemed most concerned with the new narrative. She felt strongly that it would be best to delay it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她好像很担心新故事线，她觉得最好能推迟上线。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, grandpa, what the hell was the delay back there？I just punch the tickets, Sir. You should punch your face…
yingyinNormal.zh: 老头，怎么晚点了？我只负责在票上打孔。你应该打你的头。。。

yingyinNormal.en: The ambassador is working hard to push the peacekeeping resolution to a vote by the General Assembly. Why the delay?
yingyinNormal.zh: 大使在努力推动联合国大会就维和提案投票 。为什么延迟了？

yingyinNormal.en: Are we gonna make up the ten minute？We gonna try, Sir. Are you talking about Brian？Hey Grandpa, what the hell was the delay back there？
yingyinNormal.zh: 晚点的十分钟能追回来吧？先生，我们尽量。你是在说布莱恩的事吗？老头，怎么晚点了？

yingyinNormal.en: After a delay, the stock market began a big bull market that lasted 18 years, and the US economy enjoyed the greatest growth period in its history. This experience was like a blow to my head with a baseball bat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 延迟之后股票市场进入了长达18年的牛市，这也是历史上美国经济发展最好的时间。这件事情对我来说是当头棒喝。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It's also a good idea to <highlight>delay</highlight> the conversation if you are in a meeting or other public space.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你在开会或在其他公共场所，最好推迟谈话。

examination_example.sentence: Starting next year, any guaranteed bonus of top executives could be <highlight>delayed</highlight> 10 years if their banks are under investigation for wrongdoing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从明年开始，如果银行因不法行为受到调查，那么已经承诺给银行高管的奖金都可能会推迟10年发放。

examination_example.sentence: Sometimes storms blew the vessels far off their course, and often calm brought unbearably long <highlight>delay</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有时暴风雨会把船只吹离航道很远，而风平浪静常常会带来令人难以忍受的长时间延误。

examination_example.sentence: There could be significant traffic <highlight>delays</highlight>, so please start to plan your journey now.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为可能会有严重的交通延误，所以请现在就开始计划你的旅程。

examination_example.sentence: For women, <highlight>delayed</highlight> marriage — which is related, in part, to labor market outcomes for men — may explain more of the increase in their living in the family home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于女性来说，推迟结婚——在一定程度上与男性在劳动力市场上就业情形有关——可能更能解释为什么越来越多的女性住在父母家。

examination_example.sentence: The result is that the commitments that previously characterized the beginning of adulthood are now being <highlight>delayed</highlight>, and new patterns of behavior and a new stage of life are emerging for those in their twenties.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 结果是，以前标志着成年期开始的责任如今被推迟履行，二十多岁的年轻群体中开始出现新的行为方式和新的生活阶段。
